title: 200 - The Future of the American Church - With Skye Jethani
description:
The Road to 200 ends here! Our third part of "The Future of the American Church" concludes with an amazing conversation with Skye Jethani. Where are we going? Where have we been and why are we where we are right now? All of these are discussed. As always, thank you for listening!
